import org.apache.spark.mllib.recommendation.ALS
        import org.apache.spark.mllib.recommendation.MatrixFactorizationModel
        import org.apache.spark.mllib.recommendation.Rating
        import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.StringIndexer
        import org.apache.spark.sql.Row
        
        val parquetFileClick = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypsodata/click/fr/2016/*/*/*.parquet")
        val clickedoffers = parquetFileClick.select("userId", "offerViewId", "clickId")
        val clickedValidOffers = clickedoffers.filter(!($"offerViewId".isNull))
        val indexerUserId = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("userId").setOutputCol("user")
        val indexerOfferId = new StringIndexer().setInputCol("offerViewId").setOutputCol("offer") 
        val clickedOffersIndexedUsers = indexerUserId.fit(clickedValidOffers).transform(clickedValidOffers)
        val clickedOffersIndexedOffers = indexerOfferId.fit(clickedOffersIndexedUsers).transform(clickedOffersIndexedUsers)
        val groupedOffers = clickedOffersIndexedOffers.groupBy("user","offer").count
        z.show(groupedOffers)
